                            <comment id="12934664" author="streamy" created="Mon, 22 Nov 2010 23:52:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yeah this is something I had to add a lot of checks for in HMaster as well.  +1 on adding null checks before we stop/interrupt stuff.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12935027" author="stack" created="Tue, 23 Nov 2010 20:21:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 on adding nullcheck.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sequence in which stuff is started was undergoing high velocity change up to the end.  Not surprised holes if start sequence aborted midway.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12935074" author="jdcryans" created="Tue, 23 Nov 2010 22:00:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch attached just adds a bunch of null checks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
